title: Hour 3 - NFL & College Football Matchups, Duane Rankin

description:
Dan and the Danettes discuss the most interesting matchups we can look forward to watching this weekend, and Dan talks to Phoenix Suns Insider, Duane Rankin about the mood in the locker room after owner Robert Sarver got off relatively easy for violating workplace standards.
